  "system": {
    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Ember Kin are young Fire Nephilim — large, hot, and straightforward. They advance and hit things. Their Heat Aura is a minor hazard rather than a primary threat at this tier. A summoner who needs a Large creature that frightens enemies through sheer physical presence and hits harder than anything of equivalent TR will find them adequate. They understand simple instructions and execute them without embellishment.</p>"
