    "attacksNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Slam [Combat]:</strong> Melee attack (Agi 3 + Melee Combat 4), Reach: 10 ft\n<ul>\n<li><em>Margin 1:</em> 10 damage (Large, standard natural: 8 + 2) + 2 fire damage (Half DR)</li>\n<li><em>Margin 2:</em> 15 damage (10 + 5 Str) + 2 fire damage; target gains Singed condition</li>\n<li><em>Margin 3:</em> 15 damage + 2 fire damage; target gains Ignited condition</li>\n</ul></li>\n<li><strong>Rock Throw [Combat]:</strong> Ranged attack (Dex 2 + Ranged Combat 1), Range: 40/80 ft\n<ul>\n<li><em>Margin 1:</em> 8 damage</li>\n<li><em>Margin 2:</em> 8 damage; target knocked Prone</li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul>",
